<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gatewaydoc Mail Template</title>
    
</head>
<body>
    <section class="main" style="margin-top: 80px;border: 1px solid transparent; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.5em;" >
        <div class="first" style="padding: 10px; height: 60px; background-color: rgba(79, 177, 201, 0.966); border-radius: 20px 20px 0px 0px;">
            <h1 style="color: white; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">Gatewaydoc</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="second" style="padding: 25px; padding-left: 30px; background-color: rgba(5, 199, 247, 0.048);">
            <p class="body">
                <span class="title" style="font-weight: bold;">Bonjour,<br><br></span>
                Merci de faire confiance à Gatewaydoc pour votre santé;<br><br> 
                Afin de finaliser et de confirmer votre adresse e-mail,
                veuillez renseigner votre code de confirmation ci-dessous :<br>
                <div class="code" style="width: 100px; height: 50px; padding: 15px; background-color:  rgba(79, 177, 201, 0.966); color: white; text-align: center;  
                    @media screen and (min-width: 481px) {
    
                    .main{
                        width: 100%;
                    }
                    .code{
                        margin-bottom: 15px;
                    }
                  }
                  @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
                    .main{
                        width: 100%;
                    
                    }
                    .code{
                        margin-bottom: 15px;
                    }
                    
                }
                  "><%= code %><br></div>
            </p>
            <p class="footer" >
                <span class="merci" style="font-weight: bold;">Merci,<br></span>
                Gatewaydoc
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="last" style="padding: 20px; padding-left: 30px; background-color:#2c3e50; color: white; border: 1px solid transparent;  height: 60px;border-radius: 0px 0px 20px 20px;  ">
            <h4 style="font-size: 0.8em; margin: 2px;">Besoin d'aide?</h4>
            <h6 style="padding-top: 5px; font-size: 0.7em; margin: 2px;">N'hésitez pas à contacter notre service client</h6>
            <a href="https://www.gatewaydoc.com/contact" style="font-size: 0.7em; color: rgba(79, 177, 201, 0.966);">Contactez-nous</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>